I was listening to this last month during my cruise outside on the beach chairs and I didn't realise but I was dancing. When I looked up, my parents were telling me that I was dancing during listening to the song. I felt so embarrassed because everyone was staring at me but they started applauding and I felt over- the- moon and not embarrassed. No- one knew what I was listening to so I told my parents. On Friday for my birthday when I was cutting my cake, they put it Nothing Else Matters on and I was so tempted to dance but I got through it and danced after. Thanks to that time, I now know what I am capable of and I am trying to get better by taking dancing lessons!!!! I always think about the time on the cruise ever since it happened and I listen to this piece of music!!! I find this song so inspiring as it gave me a new talent which I never knew I had before. I also find it inspiring because I am British so I look up to them and make me always think good.

Jesy is an amazing person, very beautiful inside and outside, kind, caring, super hot 😉, defiantly very inspirational, she is sooooo talented, she can be amazingly and hilariously crazy but she can also be very sensible when she needs to be, and no matter what people say about her, she shouldn't listen to them, because she one of the most amazing people in the world, she's inspired hundreds, and personally I'm so proud of how much she's grown through the years.

Jade is really beautiful inside and out, kind, caring, her accent is amazing, super hot 😉😅, very talented, she is so funny, and no matter what people may say things about her, they are just jealous of how amazing and beautiful and talented she is, and I am so proud of her.

Perrie is beautiful inside and outside,  kind, caring, super talented, super hot 😉😆(just like all of them) she is so hillarious 😂 and she is an inspiration to so many people, including me. And like the other 2, no matter what people would say about her, she should take no notice at all, because she's great.

Leigh-Ann is beautiful inside and out, kind caring ( and like all the others ) super hot, soooooo talented, her voice can be so emotional and it's so amazing, she is so inspiring, she is so funny and just like all the others she shouldn't take notice of what people may say about her, cause she's awesome. 

These four beautiful girls are the most amazing people ever, they have come so far, they have worked so hard. I love that they love each other so much, and how much they care and love their fans and supporters, whenever I see videos of them crying I just want to reach through the screen and give them a huge hug, they deserve so much, if it wasn't for little mix I wouldn't have had the inspiration to start writing my own songs and singing them in front of people. I listen to  their songs everyday, they are one of my favourite bands of all time, and if it wasn't for them I wouldn't be who I am now, I am so much confident because of them and their inspiration, I love you Little Mix- never give up!
